702794f-a.title: Brooklyn: 60th Street - 10th Avenue
702794f-a.text:
60th Street, south side, west from (No. 1012) and
across 10th Avenue, showing a W. P. A. sewer project.
The three-story houses tn the right background are on
the west side of Fort Hamilton Avenue.
October 28, 1936
Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE
